sequenceDiagram
    participant Dev as Developer
    participant GH as GitHub<br/>rhoai-3.0 branch
    participant Renovate as Renovate/<br/>Dependabot
    participant GHA as GitHub Actions<br/>process-operator-bundle
    participant PAC as PipelinesAsCode<br/>Webhook
    participant Tekton as Tekton PipelineRun<br/>Konflux CI/CD
    participant EC as Enterprise Contract<br/>Compliance
    participant Quay as quay.io<br/>443/TCP HTTPS
    participant RHIO as registry.redhat.io<br/>443/TCP HTTPS

    Note over Dev,RHIO: Flow 1: Operator Bundle Build (Konflux/Tekton)
    Dev->>GH: Push to rhoai-3.0 branch
    GH->>PAC: Webhook notification<br/>443/TCP HTTPS TLS 1.2+
    PAC->>Tekton: Trigger PipelineRun
    Tekton->>GH: git clone<br/>443/TCP HTTPS<br/>Auth: git_auth_secret
    Tekton->>Tekton: Build bundle image<br/>(FROM scratch)
    Tekton->>Quay: Push odh-operator-bundle<br/>443/TCP HTTPS<br/>Auth: Registry credentials
    Tekton->>Tekton: Trigger FBC rebuild<br/>via catalog-patch.yaml

    Note over Dev,RHIO: Flow 2: Bundle Patch Automation (GitHub Actions)
    Renovate->>GH: Create PR with<br/>updated image digests<br/>443/TCP HTTPS
    Dev->>GH: Merge PR
    GH->>GHA: Trigger workflow
    GHA->>GHA: Process bundle patches<br/>Update CSV with new digests
    GHA->>GH: Commit updated bundle<br/>443/TCP HTTPS<br/>Auth: GitHub Token

    Note over Dev,RHIO: Flow 3: Release Pipeline
    Dev->>Tekton: Trigger release
    Tekton->>EC: Enterprise Contract validation
    EC->>Quay: Cosign signature verification<br/>443/TCP HTTPS TLS 1.2+<br/>Auth: Public key
    EC-->>Tekton: Validation result
    Tekton->>Quay: Stage release<br/>443/TCP HTTPS<br/>Auth: Registry credentials
    Tekton->>RHIO: Production release<br/>443/TCP HTTPS<br/>Auth: Registry credentials

    Note over Dev,RHIO: Flow 4: OLM Installation (Target Cluster)
    Note right of RHIO: OLM discovers operator<br/>via FBC catalog fragment
    RHIO-->>Tekton: Pull bundle image
    Note right of Tekton: OLM unpacks bundle,<br/>installs CSV + CRDs,<br/>deploys rhods-operator
